========
Download
========
.. Note::

   **If you are a user** willing to try AROS, please use the links in **Distributions**
   section to download a fully featured AROS distribution. The nightly builds you
   will find at the bottom of the page are only meant for developers. The nighly builds
   are not configured to be easily used, sometimes are not stable and they miss most 
